OOC: Alright... I got absolutely zero questions about Aerotaur's new name... 
So... here it is.  I got bored and thought he should have a more appropriate 
name for his new look... In short Hevngjerrig is Norwegian for Vengeful.  On 
a side note Hevn is Norwegian for Revenge.

::Hevngjerrig::
       He continues to hold onto Blackstorm's shoulder.  "I'm afraid that 
isn't good enough.  You are the reason I am here.  I exist only to ensure 
your well-being."  He gives her shoulder a quick squeeze and lets go, turning 
to face Maxima again.

       "As for you, I really don't care what Hydras thinks of my new look.  I 
don't think we're that similar.  I mean come on, he's a two headed dragon, 
and I'm a winged centaur.  How much more different can you get?"  He leans 
close to her and smiles amicably.  "As for this form,"  he shrugs, "is it my 
fault if we have similar tastes?"  He winks conspiratorially and backs up a 
step.

--part1_103.2d0dd073.2be1ecfd_boundary
